SubjectLoran-C Station Port Hardy BC 1979 Termination of Treaty (US) #9
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to terminate for Canada the EXCHANGE OF NOTES between Canada and the United States of America constituting an Agreement providing for the Establishment of a Loran-C Station in the vicinity of Port Hardy, Vancouver Island, B. C., done on 19 and 29 March 1979.
